# Node.js API Module

{{ project_name }} includes a Node.js API built with [Fastify](https://fastify.io/).

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Start development server
pnpm --filter api-node dev

# Or use the provided script
./scripts/dev-api-node.sh
```

## Endpoints

The API is available at `http://localhost:3000` by default.

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/` | GET | Root endpoint |
| `/health` | GET | Health check |

## Configuration

Configure the API via environment variables:

```bash
# .env
NODE_API_HOST=0.0.0.0
NODE_API_PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development
```

## Testing

```bash
# Run API tests
pnpm --filter api-node test

# With coverage
pnpm --filter api-node test:coverage
```

